{"tid":994144,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩納哥立即解僱亨利！執教12場僅贏2場...","createTime":"2019-01-24T12:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T01:50:10.000Z","uid":32938,"like":117,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"432f02e4e7f9d08ea61d569ae78f869ea5d3274b","tid":994144,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:41:40.000Z","msg":"據《鏡報》消息，摩納哥高層對亨利已經失去了信心，亨利將在48小時內下台。同時，摩納哥高層決定請回前任主教練雅爾迪姆繼續執教球隊。<br />\n<br />\n　　亨利在中途接手摩納哥後並未創下佳績，自10月13日上任摩納哥教練以來亨利共帶隊出戰20場比賽，取得5勝4平11負的成績，其中的12場聯賽比賽中摩納哥僅勝2場，球隊目前正處於法甲降班區。<br />\n<br />\n　　據悉，為了避免球隊跌落第二級別，摩納哥高層已經決定邀請前任教練雅爾迪姆重返摩納哥。"},{"pid":"6e9eddad824ab96b1b54d6f1769ce5b6fd9b8347","tid":994144,"uid":118973,"like":214,"dislike":2,"score":212,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:42:57.000Z","msg":"一世英名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n踢波咁勁但做教練咁柒"},{"pid":"44f3b8be0ea9239af7589ff674936855f21ae919","tid":994144,"uid":18559,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:43:59.000Z","msg":"仆街 斷我米路"},{"pid":"344925e96aec12d6e3ce4dbcc5c8281d86566eb5","tid":994144,"uid":2169,"like":126,"dislike":1,"score":125,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:44:09.000Z","msg":"法比咪中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5e1cd4aead8a853afe0af864076f48ad21af0a","tid":994144,"uid":51129,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:45:32.000Z","msg":"法比啱啱先過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1efc29a39d224b28bef7f18eb44ec3354bb99ed","tid":994144,"uid":133184,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:52:08.000Z","msg":"法比仆街了"},{"pid":"ce0ca097469eb13aecb19a8cd34d33edf755124f","tid":994144,"uid":45335,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T12:53:21.000Z","msg":"同加利狗一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"